item.title: Hockey Ladies 1s haunt UCL
item.author: Harriet Stevenson,
item.description: On All Hallows Eve the Ladies 1’s set out to play some oldrivals UCL. UCL definitely had a point to prove as we had put them out of 2 cups last year. We went out hard in the first 10mins with a new line-up having fresher Bryony in central-midfield controlling the game. With some good play down the …
